# Implementation Plan - Order System & Inventory Management

This plan outlines the steps to build a robust e-commerce backend and frontend for TechCity, including order lifecycle, inventory tracking, security enhancements, and notifications.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Product Data Migration**: We will move all products from the hardcoded `products.js` file into the PostgreSQL database. This allows for real-time stock management but means you will manage products via the Admin Dashboard instead of editing JS files.

> [!NOTE]
> **Notifications**: I will implement email notifications using `nodemailer`. You will need to provide SMTP credentials (e.g., for Gmail or a professional email service) in the `.env` file later.

