## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test order creation with `test_api.cjs` (mocking stock checks).
- Verify stock decrement after a successful checkout.
- Check that Admin can update order status.

### Manual Verification
- Place a test order as a user.
- View the order in the Admin dashboard and change status to "Shipped".
- Verify that the User dashboard shows the updated status.
- Attempt to buy an "out of stock" product and verify the button is disabled.
